name: I Am Harlequin
description: This is the LIMITED EDITION (500) of I Am Harlequin's first double A side with artwork by the artist herself. Tracks and Covers: I Am Harlequin - The Liberty I Am Harlequin - The King's Daughter All tracks written and produced by Anne Freier. Photography by Rossella Vanon Artwork by Anne Freier OFFICIALLY LAUNCHED 31. OCTOBER 2011. Don't forget to get your free downloads of 'Marianne' and 'Bette Davis Eyes' here: Download
